Silk quilts with weight gain treatment that are more inelastic
More fluffy and elastic!
Friendly reminder:
There are silk quilts on the market that have poor bulkiness and elasticity, and are weight-added.
Silk is sold by the weight of the silk.
Now unscrupulous merchants illegally use silk floss to increase weight,
A 4 catty silk quilt may only have 3 catties of silk,
The remaining 1 catty is a lubricating oily chemical weighting agent adsorbed on the silk fiber.
After testing, the content of basic protein amino acids is seriously substandard.
src: 比无弹性的增重处理的蚕丝被
更有蓬松性 更有弹性！
友情提醒：市场上有蓬松度弹性很差的蚕丝被，有增重处理，蚕丝都是按蚕丝重量卖的，现有不法商家违法使用丝绵增重处理，可能4斤的蚕丝被，只有3斤的蚕丝，余下1斤是吸附在蚕丝纤维上的润滑油性化学增重剂。
经检测，基蛋白质氨基酸含量严重不达标。
